      "description": "Hey there! You honestly have to see this car to believe it. It\u2019s been my absolute pride and joy, kept in a climate-controlled garage and pampered since day one. It looks and drives like it just rolled off the showroom floor\u2014not a single scratch or speck of dust anywhere! If you\u2019re looking for a ride that\u2019s basically brand new without the dealership price tag, this is the one for you. Come take a look, you won't be disappointed!",
