      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Offering a pristine E46 M3 featuring the high-revving S54 power plant with individual throttle bodies and dual-VANOS timing. This example is mechanically sorted with documented rod bearing service and a reinforced rear subframe. The chassis remains taut, benefiting from a 6-speed manual gearbox and a factory limited-slip differential. Every bushing and seal is intact, and the paint depth is consistent across all panels. A rare, turn-key investment for those seeking peak BMW M-division engineering.",
